#MATERIALS AND RIGHTS
Once submitted for the festival, the subscription cannot be deleted. 
The selected artists will be asked for the movie-file in the most suitable media for the projection. 
Any shipping costs for physical media (if necessary) will be charged to the artists. 
The submitted works will become part of the festival archive. 
The works can be used for promotional purposes of the Nanometri Festival. 
Any other use will be communicated to the author and authorized by the author himself.

